Hi all, I'm Endrit, 29 years old (in my 16th year, haha, just a joke!), a medical student studying in lovely Italy.
The gadget you can see above my glasses is the Luminette Light Therapy Glasses—it replicates the effect of sunlight to enhance your energy and concentration.

I really think that studying can be made easier and more enjoyable with good company. And so, I'm here for the purpose of connecting, inspiring, and growing with all of you. Let's make studying a positive, rewarding, and perhaps even enjoyable thing.
